:EthicalPrinciple_GodsDoNotHonorWicked_284_288
  a owl:NamedIndividual, :EthicalPrinciple ;
  :description "Creon’s reasoning: the gods do not honor wicked men—especially one who came to burn temples, offerings, land, and scatter laws."^^xsd:string .

:EthicalPrinciple_MoneyCorrupts_295_301
